5:["$","div",null,{"className":"x:mx-auto x:flex x:max-w-(--nextra-content-width)","children":["$","$L1f",null,{"value":[{"value":"待规划功能","id":"待规划功能","depth":2},{"value":"📱 Telegram Mini App 集成","id":"-telegram-mini-app-集成","depth":3},{"value":"已完成功能","id":"已完成功能","depth":2}],"children":[["$","$L20",null,{}],["$","$L21",null,{"metadata":{"title":"开发路线图 / Roadmap","filePath":"content/roadmap.mdx"},"bottomContent":"$undefined","sourceCode":"# 开发路线图 / Roadmap\n\n待规划和待实现的功能点，按优先级和依赖关系排列。\n\n---\n\n## 待规划功能\n\n### 📱 Telegram Mini App 集成\n\n**优先级：** 待定（需先完成部署上线）  \n**依赖：** HTTPS 域名 + 服务器部署\n\n**方案：** Telegram Mini App（方案一）\n\n将现有 Next.js 游戏前端以 Mini App 形式嵌入 Telegram，用户可直接在 Telegram 内打开并游玩。\n\n**核心改动点：**\n\n| 模块 | 改动内容 |\n|------|----------|\n| Bot 注册 | 通过 `@BotFather` 创建 Bot，绑定 Mini App 域名 |\n| 后端登录 | 新增 `POST /auth/telegram` 接口，验证 Telegram `initData` HMAC 签名，自动注册/登录用户 |\n| 前端 SDK | 引入 `@twa-dev/sdk`，初始化 `WebApp.ready()`，适配主题色与安全区域 |\n| 单点登录 | Telegram userId 作为唯一标识，与现有单点登录系统集成 |\n| 支付（可选）| 使用 Telegram Payments API 实现筹码充值（Stars 或第三方支付）|\n\n**参考文档：**\n- https://core.telegram.org/bots/webapps\n- https://github.com/twa-dev/SDK\n\n---\n\n## 已完成功能\n\n- 单点登录（同一账号同时只能在一个设备登录）\n- 顶出旧设备并自动登出（WebSocket `force_logout` 事件）\n- 游戏重连支持（断线重连 + `rejoin_available` 事件）","children":[["$","div",null,{"id":"nextra-skip-nav"}],["$","main",null,{"data-pagefind-body":true,"children":[["$","h1",null,{"id":"$undefined","className":"x:tracking-tight x:text-slate-900 x:dark:text-slate-100 x:font-bold x:mt-2 x:text-4xl","children":["开发路线图 / Roadmap","$undefined"]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"className":"x:not-first:mt-[1.25em] x:leading-7","children":"待规划和待实现的功能点，按优先级和依赖关系排列。"}],"\n",["$","hr",null,{"className":"x:my-[2em] nextra-border"}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"待规划功能","className":"x:tracking-tight x:text-slate-900 x:dark:text-slate-100 x:font-semibold x:target:animate-[fade-in_1.5s] x:mt-10 x:border-b x:pb-1 x:text-3xl nextra-border","children":["待规划功能",["$","$L22",null,{"id":"待规划功能"}]]}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"-telegram-mini-app-集成","className":"x:tracking-tight x:text-slate-900 x:dark:text-slate-100 x:font-semibold x:target:animate-[fade-in_1.5s] x:mt-8 x:text-2xl","children":["📱 Telegram Mini App 集成",["$","$L22",null,{"id":"-telegram-mini-app-集成"}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"className":"x:not-first:mt-[1.25em] x:leading-7","children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"优先级："}]," 待定（需先完成部署上线）",["$","br",null,{}],"\n",["$","strong",null,{"children":"依赖："}]," HTTPS 域名 + 服务器部署"]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"className":"x:not-first:mt-[1.25em] x:leading-7","children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"方案："}]," Telegram Mini App（方案一）"]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"className":"x:not-first:mt-[1.25em] x:leading-7","children":"将现有 Next.js 游戏前端以 Mini App 形式嵌入 Telegram，用户可直接在 Telegram 内打开并游玩。"}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"className":"x:not-first:mt-[1.25em] x:leading-7","children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"核心改动点："}]}],"\n",["$","table",null,{"className":"x:block x:overflow-x-auto nextra-scrollbar x:not-first:mt-[1.25em] x:p-0","children":[["$","thead",null,{"children":["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","th",null,{"children":"模块","className":"x:m-0 x:border x:border-gray-300 x:px-4 x:py-2 x:font-semibold x:dark:border-gray-600"}],["$","th",null,{"children":"改动内容","className":"x:m-0 x:border x:border-gray-300 x:px-4 x:py-2 x:font-semibold x:dark:border-gray-600"}]],"className":"x:m-0 x:border-t x:border-gray-300 x:p-0 x:dark:border-gray-600 x:even:bg-gray-100 x:even:dark:bg-gray-600/20"}]}],["$","tbody",null,{"children":[["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"Bot 注册","className":"x:m-0 x:border x:border-gray-300 x:px-4 x:py-2 x:dark:border-gray-600"}],["$","td",null,{"children":["通过 ",["$","code",null,{"className":"nextra-code","dir":"ltr","children":"@BotFather"}]," 创建 Bot，绑定 Mini App 域名"],"className":"x:m-0 x:border x:border-gray-300 x:px-4 x:py-2 x:dark:border-gray-600"}]],"className":"x:m-0 x:border-t x:border-gray-300 x:p-0 x:dark:border-gray-600 x:even:bg-gray-100 x: